explanation: [0-0] A white coffee cup sits on a marble countertop, filled with freshly made latte, the surface a uniform brown.

[0-10] A hand holds a metal latte art needle, the tip picks up some milk foam, and spreads it evenly from the edge of the coffee cup. Then, a small dark bottle with a slender nozzle is picked up, and dark sauce is drizzled onto the milk foam. The hand draws three concentric circles of decreasing size on the surface of the coffee with the bottle. Finally, a white dot is dotted in the center of the three concentric circles on the coffee surface with a latte art needle.
